reagovať len na meno Seol.

74
00:05:12,945 --> 00:05:15,015
- Pani Kang.
- Pán Han.

75
00:05:15,615 --> 00:05:16,915
Mali by ste si to priznať.

76
00:05:17,115 --> 00:05:18,645
